author: julianfoad
msg: On the 'move-tracking-2' branch: Teach 'svnmover update' to merge the
local changes into the new revision.
This does not handle conflicts. If a conflict occurs in the merge, the merge
bails out at that point. Any local changes merged before that point are
retained and the rest of the local changes are lost.
(do_update): Move further down the file. Merge local changes.
(execute): Add syntax checking for the 'update' command parameter.
